WEBVTT

00:00:00.910 --> 00:00:02.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>DECEMBER 4TH - SHONAN PERSONAL
INSTRUCTION CRAM SCHOOL</b></Default>

00:00:03.040 --> 00:00:04.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Thanks for today, Mr. Sakuta.</b></Default>

00:00:04.830 --> 00:00:07.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah. Just don't forget to go
over what we reviewed today.</b></Default>

00:00:07.370 --> 00:00:09.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You don't gotta remind me.</b></Default>

00:00:09.410 --> 00:00:11.199 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[grunts] See ya.
-[thuds]</b></Default>

00:00:18.079 --> 00:00:19.449 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You too, Mr. Sakuta.</b></Default>

00:00:19.539 --> 00:00:22.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That homework I gave you?
Don't forget about it, okay?</b></Default>

00:00:26.500 --> 00:00:29.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Then I'll say this is homework
from me to you.</b></Default>

00:00:29.250 --> 00:00:31.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Please think about what kind
of puberty syndrome it is</b></Default>

00:00:31.789 --> 00:00:32.869 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and figure it out.</b></Default>

00:00:33.409 --> 00:00:34.909 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Man, I'm in a bind.</b></Default>

00:00:35.409 --> 00:00:36.659 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Azusagawa?</b></Default>

00:00:37.450 --> 00:00:39.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Could I get your advice
on something?</b></Default>

00:00:40.329 --> 00:00:41.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

00:00:42.619 --> 00:00:44.869 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[♪ opening theme song playing]</b></Default>

00:01:50.540 --> 00:01:56.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>RASCAL DOES NOT DREAM
OF SANTA CLAUS</b></Default>

00:02:14.449 --> 00:02:16.909 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, then, what did you
want to talk about?</b></Default>

00:02:17.830 --> 00:02:19.909 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah. Actually...</b></Default>

00:02:20.370 --> 00:02:23.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What's the matter? Did someone
ask you out or something?</b></Default>

00:02:23.080 --> 00:02:24.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

00:02:25.199 --> 00:02:26.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>For real?</b></Default>

00:02:27.539 --> 00:02:28.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Who was it?</b></Default>

00:02:28.949 --> 00:02:30.159 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's my student.</b></Default>

00:02:30.250 --> 00:02:31.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh.</b></Default>

00:02:31.870 --> 00:02:33.449 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>Toranosuke Kasai.</i></b></Default>

00:02:33.580 --> 00:02:35.159 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>How did you figure it out?</b></Default>

00:02:35.250 --> 00:02:37.199 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I mean, the guy's aura
was basically screaming</b></Default>

00:02:37.289 --> 00:02:38.659 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>"I love Futaba."</b></Default>

00:02:40.370 --> 00:02:41.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>When was this?</b></Default>

00:02:42.289 --> 00:02:44.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yesterday. In my classroom.</b></Default>

00:02:44.699 --> 00:02:46.449 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What led up to him asking?</b></Default>

00:02:46.949 --> 00:02:49.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I got the feeling that he hasn't
been able to concentrate</b></Default>

00:02:49.449 --> 00:02:50.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>on studying lately.</b></Default>

00:02:50.909 --> 00:02:53.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I could see that something
was weighing on his mind.</b></Default>

00:02:53.830 --> 00:02:55.699 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So I asked him what's wrong.</b></Default>

00:02:55.789 --> 00:02:58.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Okay. Did you give him
a response?</b></Default>

00:02:58.659 --> 00:02:59.659 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I couldn't.</b></Default>

00:02:59.789 --> 00:03:01.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He said, "You don't have
to reply right now</b></Default>

00:03:01.870 --> 00:03:02.949 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and ran off.</b></Default>

00:03:03.039 --> 00:03:04.159 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I see.</b></Default>

00:03:04.580 --> 00:03:06.199 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What do you think
I should do here?</b></Default>

00:03:06.289 --> 00:03:08.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I think you should
follow your heart, Futaba.</b></Default>

00:03:09.289 --> 00:03:10.949 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I never even thought about it.</b></Default>

00:03:11.039 --> 00:03:12.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Then you can take
this opportunity</b></Default>

00:03:12.659 --> 00:03:13.909 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to figure your thoughts out.</b></Default>

00:03:14.039 --> 00:03:16.199 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Dragging your feelings
for Kunimi forever</b></Default>

00:03:16.289 --> 00:03:17.449 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>isn't doing you any favors.</b></Default>

00:03:17.580 --> 00:03:19.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm not dragging those feelings.</b></Default>

00:03:21.039 --> 00:03:23.159 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MAI] <i>I made a reservation</i>
<i>for the inn at Hakone.</i></b></Default>

00:03:23.289 --> 00:03:24.699 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, you did?</b></Default>

00:03:24.789 --> 00:03:25.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>For the 24th?</b></Default>

00:03:25.949 --> 00:03:28.159 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Right. But since you're
going on that date</b></Default>

00:03:28.250 --> 00:03:29.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>with your cute new student</b></Default>

00:03:29.909 --> 00:03:31.699 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm not sure
if you can still go or not.</b></Default>

00:03:31.789 --> 00:03:34.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll be going, no doubt.</b></Default>

00:03:36.370 --> 00:03:37.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[sighs]</b></Default>

00:03:38.199 --> 00:03:41.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I just have to make sure to
finish my homework before then.</b></Default>

00:03:41.830 --> 00:03:43.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>DECEMBER 9TH</b></Default>

00:03:45.199 --> 00:03:47.199 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[sighs]
They're everywhere lately.</b></Default>

00:03:47.330 --> 00:03:48.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] Hmm?</b></Default>

00:03:48.949 --> 00:03:50.409 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What are you talking about?</b></Default>

00:03:50.500 --> 00:03:52.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Couples flaunting their love.</b></Default>

00:03:53.449 --> 00:03:55.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Lovers' season is coming up</b></Default>

00:03:55.080 --> 00:03:56.949 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>with the rush
of incoming events.</b></Default>

00:03:57.539 --> 00:03:59.909 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What rush of events
are you talking about?</b></Default>

00:04:00.000 --> 00:04:02.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I mean, there's Christmas Eve
and Christmas Day.</b></Default>

00:04:02.370 --> 00:04:04.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Wouldn't those just
be considered as one holiday?</b></Default>

00:04:05.000 --> 00:04:07.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Then New Year's Eve
and New Year's Day.</b></Default>

00:04:07.199 --> 00:04:08.409 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Then there's Setsubun.</b></Default>

00:04:08.500 --> 00:04:10.409 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Do couples
celebrate that, though?</b></Default>

00:04:12.289 --> 00:04:13.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh...</b></Default>

00:04:13.699 --> 00:04:15.409 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Whoa, dude. What's the matter?</b></Default>

00:04:15.699 --> 00:04:17.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm gonna cheat
on my homework a bit.</b></Default>

00:04:30.040 --> 00:04:30.949 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[sighs]</b></Default>

00:04:32.370 --> 00:04:34.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What are you doing over there?</b></Default>

00:04:36.790 --> 00:04:38.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm trying to film
video materials</b></Default>

00:04:38.500 --> 00:04:39.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>for my Christmas song.</b></Default>

00:04:40.410 --> 00:04:41.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[clatters]
-[girl groans]</b></Default>

00:04:41.449 --> 00:04:43.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Should I give you a hand?</b></Default>

00:04:48.079 --> 00:04:50.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Okay. Then just hit record
and follow me.</b></Default>

00:04:58.949 --> 00:05:00.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Is it all right
if I talk to you?</b></Default>

00:05:01.410 --> 00:05:03.949 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm only using the video
from this, so it's fine.</b></Default>

00:05:04.040 --> 00:05:05.949 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But no troublesome topics, okay?</b></Default>

00:05:06.290 --> 00:05:08.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>In that case</b></Default>

00:05:08.120 --> 00:05:10.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>about Sara Himeji's
puberty syndrome?</b></Default>

00:05:10.410 --> 00:05:11.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Who is that?</b></Default>

00:05:11.449 --> 00:05:12.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She's one of my students.</b></Default>

00:05:12.910 --> 00:05:15.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And why would
I know that, exactly?</b></Default>

00:05:15.699 --> 00:05:17.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Because apparently</b></Default>

00:05:17.370 --> 00:05:19.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that she has a case
of puberty syndrome.</b></Default>

00:05:19.410 --> 00:05:20.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Okay, and?</b></Default>

00:05:20.449 --> 00:05:22.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If it was a present
from you, Kirishima</b></Default>

00:05:22.949 --> 00:05:24.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I thought you might
know something about it.</b></Default>

00:05:25.750 --> 00:05:26.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No clue.</b></Default>

00:05:31.079 --> 00:05:34.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But you knew about Hirokawa
and Akagi, though, didn't you?</b></Default>

00:05:34.160 --> 00:05:36.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's because they go
to this university.</b></Default>

00:05:38.410 --> 00:05:41.199 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I guess I failed at cheating
on my homework.</b></Default>

00:05:41.620 --> 00:05:42.699 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Thanks, though.</b></Default>

00:05:42.790 --> 00:05:44.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I got some good footage here.</b></Default>

00:05:44.410 --> 00:05:46.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, whenever you need
a cameraman</b></Default>

00:05:46.199 --> 00:05:47.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm just a phone call away.</b></Default>

00:05:47.910 --> 00:05:48.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Really?</b></Default>

00:05:49.000 --> 00:05:50.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll hold you to that then.</b></Default>

00:05:50.910 --> 00:05:52.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm livestreaming on the 24th.</b></Default>

00:05:52.449 --> 00:05:53.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Meet here at 4:00 p.m.</b></Default>

00:05:54.000 --> 00:05:55.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No, I've got plans
on that day!</b></Default>

00:05:55.699 --> 00:05:56.949 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>See you then!</b></Default>

00:05:59.199 --> 00:06:00.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Please don't make the 24th</b></Default>

00:06:00.660 --> 00:06:02.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>even more complicated
than it already is.</b></Default>

00:06:03.410 --> 00:06:04.449 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>DECEMBER 10TH</b></Default>

00:06:04.540 --> 00:06:05.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>Hello and welcome</b></Default>

00:06:06.000 --> 00:06:07.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>This is Mai Sakurajima.</i></b></Default>

00:06:07.500 --> 00:06:09.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Um, Mr. Azusagawa?
-Huh?</b></Default>

00:06:12.290 --> 00:06:13.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Sorry to stop you.</b></Default>

00:06:13.750 --> 00:06:15.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, hey. Kasai, right?</b></Default>

00:06:16.370 --> 00:06:19.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Do you mind if I take
a little bit of your time?</b></Default>

00:06:19.079 --> 00:06:23.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's okay, but me?
Instead of Futaba?</b></Default>

00:06:29.910 --> 00:06:31.699 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So, what's this all about?</b></Default>

00:06:32.199 --> 00:06:33.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's Sara.</b></Default>

00:06:33.410 --> 00:06:35.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No, I mean, Miss Himeji.</b></Default>

00:06:36.000 --> 00:06:37.699 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Just please watch out for her.</b></Default>

00:06:38.329 --> 00:06:40.449 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What am I watching out for?</b></Default>

00:06:40.540 --> 00:06:43.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Mr. Azusagawa</b></Default>

00:06:43.449 --> 00:06:45.449 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>who's been put in charge
of Sara.</b></Default>

00:06:45.579 --> 00:06:47.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, I mean, Miss Himeji.</b></Default>

00:06:47.329 --> 00:06:50.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I think it's okay to address her
by name for now.</b></Default>

00:06:50.120 --> 00:06:51.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, okay.</b></Default>

00:06:51.579 --> 00:06:52.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If you're talking about</b></Default>

00:06:52.579 --> 00:06:55.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the professor in charge of her
before me, I know about him.</b></Default>

00:06:55.500 --> 00:06:57.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Do you know why she switched
instructors as well?</b></Default>

00:06:58.250 --> 00:06:59.199 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>From what I heard</b></Default>

00:06:59.579 --> 00:07:01.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>it's because</i>
<i>he fell in love with her.</i></b></Default>

00:07:02.540 --> 00:07:06.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Before that, the instructor
who was in charge of Sara first</b></Default>

00:07:06.120 --> 00:07:08.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>also got swapped out
for the same reason.</b></Default>

00:07:08.410 --> 00:07:09.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

00:07:09.410 --> 00:07:10.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And that's not all.</b></Default>

00:07:10.829 --> 00:07:12.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I've heard there are several
boys at our high school</b></Default>

00:07:12.910 --> 00:07:14.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>who have asked Sara out.</b></Default>

00:07:14.290 --> 00:07:16.199 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, she does seem
quite popular.</b></Default>

00:07:16.579 --> 00:07:17.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But if you're really
that worried</b></Default>

00:07:17.750 --> 00:07:19.699 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>about other guys flocking
to her like that</b></Default>

00:07:19.790 --> 00:07:21.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>why don't you
look out for her yourself?</b></Default>

00:07:21.699 --> 00:07:23.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I can't do that.</b></Default>

00:07:23.329 --> 00:07:25.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Sara and I are actually
next door neighbors</b></Default>

00:07:25.750 --> 00:07:28.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and we used to play together
a lot when we were little kids.</b></Default>

00:07:28.750 --> 00:07:30.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So, she's a childhood friend?</b></Default>

00:07:30.410 --> 00:07:32.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yes, I guess you could say that.</b></Default>

00:07:32.660 --> 00:07:34.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And so, you see, I...</b></Default>

00:07:34.250 --> 00:07:35.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Until middle school</b></Default>

00:07:35.410 --> 00:07:37.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I honestly thought
I was in love with Sara.</b></Default>

00:07:38.790 --> 00:07:41.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But then, one day</b></Default>

00:07:41.370 --> 00:07:43.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>what I had originally thought
were romantic feelings</b></Default>

00:07:43.870 --> 00:07:46.699 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>weren't even close to how
it feels to being truly in love.</b></Default>

00:07:46.790 --> 00:07:49.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And that's because you fell
in love with Futaba, right?</b></Default>

00:07:49.370 --> 00:07:50.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yes.</b></Default>

00:07:50.500 --> 00:07:51.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh? Uh...</b></Default>

00:07:55.329 --> 00:07:57.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hold on. How'd you...</b></Default>

00:07:57.120 --> 00:07:58.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You were emitting
a lovey-dovey aura</b></Default>

00:07:58.949 --> 00:08:00.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>when asking her for help
at the cram school.</b></Default>

00:08:01.040 --> 00:08:01.949 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[grunts nervously]</b></Default>

00:08:02.040 --> 00:08:04.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Futaba's a formidable opponent</b></Default>

00:08:05.040 --> 00:08:06.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Uh, okay.</b></Default>

00:08:06.620 --> 00:08:08.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's not what I wanted
to talk about right now.</b></Default>

00:08:08.829 --> 00:08:11.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So, let's see if I got
the story straight.</b></Default>

00:08:11.199 --> 00:08:13.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Ever since that day
when you dumped Himeji--</b></Default>

00:08:13.449 --> 00:08:14.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I did not dump her.</b></Default>

00:08:15.620 --> 00:08:17.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>For practical purposes, you did.</b></Default>

00:08:17.660 --> 00:08:19.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And now you're worried
because you dumped her</b></Default>

00:08:19.500 --> 00:08:22.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Himeji's oddly popular with guys
for some reason.</b></Default>

00:08:22.160 --> 00:08:23.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah.</b></Default>

00:08:23.250 --> 00:08:25.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's why I wanted to ask you
to please watch out for her.</b></Default>

00:08:25.949 --> 00:08:28.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But why are you consulting me?</b></Default>

00:08:28.160 --> 00:08:30.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, I tried consulting
with Kunimi</b></Default>

00:08:30.370 --> 00:08:32.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but then he told me
that I should count on you.</b></Default>

00:08:33.080 --> 00:08:36.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Kunimi only says stuff
he doesn't need to say.</b></Default>

00:08:38.080 --> 00:08:40.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] Do you have
Futaba's class today?</b></Default>

00:08:40.080 --> 00:08:41.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yes. But actually</b></Default>

00:08:41.409 --> 00:08:43.659 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm not pursuing
Miss Futaba anymore.</b></Default>

00:08:43.750 --> 00:08:44.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why is that?</b></Default>

00:08:44.909 --> 00:08:47.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You know about the dreaming tag
that's trending, right?</b></Default>

00:08:48.289 --> 00:08:49.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, I had a dream
the other night</b></Default>

00:08:49.830 --> 00:08:52.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that Miss Futaba dumped me
on Christmas Eve.</b></Default>

00:08:52.370 --> 00:08:54.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The dreaded 24th strikes again.</b></Default>

00:08:55.200 --> 00:08:58.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So, what did Futaba say
in the dream?</b></Default>

00:08:58.200 --> 00:09:00.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She told me, "I can't date
one of my students."</b></Default>

00:09:01.039 --> 00:09:02.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>SHONAN PERSONAL INSTRUCTION
CRAM SCHOOL</b></Default>

00:09:02.080 --> 00:09:03.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And you're giving up
just like that?</b></Default>

00:09:03.580 --> 00:09:06.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If I'm being honest with you</b></Default>

00:09:07.289 --> 00:09:08.909 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>After having a dream like that</b></Default>

00:09:09.000 --> 00:09:11.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>it's like I'm thinking about her
even more now.</b></Default>

00:09:11.659 --> 00:09:12.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If it were me</b></Default>

00:09:12.870 --> 00:09:15.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'd say, "If I'm accepted
to my first-choice university</b></Default>

00:09:15.620 --> 00:09:16.659 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>please date me."</b></Default>

00:09:17.080 --> 00:09:18.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Uh...
-Of course</b></Default>

00:09:18.370 --> 00:09:20.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>only if you're serious
about Futaba.</b></Default>

00:09:20.450 --> 00:09:22.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Uh, okay. I'll do my best.</b></Default>

00:09:23.159 --> 00:09:25.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh? My apologies.</b></Default>

00:09:25.120 --> 00:09:26.909 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I have to get going now.</b></Default>

00:09:28.950 --> 00:09:29.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[Sakuta sighs]</b></Default>

00:09:31.039 --> 00:09:32.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Azusagawa.</b></Default>

00:09:32.330 --> 00:09:33.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hey, Futaba.</b></Default>

00:09:34.200 --> 00:09:36.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What were you talking
to Kasai about?</b></Default>

00:09:36.409 --> 00:09:38.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He told me they're
childhood friends.</b></Default>

00:09:38.370 --> 00:09:40.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Wait, what? Who is?</b></Default>

00:09:40.159 --> 00:09:42.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Kasai and Himeji, apparently.</b></Default>

00:09:42.409 --> 00:09:44.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So we had a little chat
about it.</b></Default>

00:09:44.620 --> 00:09:46.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You say anything unnecessary?</b></Default>

00:09:47.000 --> 00:09:49.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I only said the necessary stuff.</b></Default>

00:09:49.289 --> 00:09:51.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's probably
what was unnecessary.</b></Default>

00:09:51.659 --> 00:09:53.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Huh?
-Mr. Sakuta!</b></Default>

00:09:53.159 --> 00:09:54.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[panting]</b></Default>

00:09:56.120 --> 00:09:57.909 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>My test, I aced it.</b></Default>

00:09:58.500 --> 00:09:59.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

00:09:59.539 --> 00:10:01.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That sure does me in.</b></Default>

00:10:01.200 --> 00:10:02.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>My lesson plan today</b></Default>

00:10:02.330 --> 00:10:04.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>was to go over the problems
you guys got wrong</b></Default>

00:10:04.409 --> 00:10:05.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>on your exams.</b></Default>

00:10:05.539 --> 00:10:07.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Aren't you going
to compliment me?</b></Default>

00:10:07.830 --> 00:10:09.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Congrats. You did a great job.</b></Default>

00:10:10.250 --> 00:10:11.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, go on ahead.</b></Default>

00:10:12.330 --> 00:10:14.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, we're going the same way.</b></Default>

00:10:19.580 --> 00:10:21.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Chilly night, isn't it?</b></Default>

00:10:21.830 --> 00:10:22.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It is.</b></Default>

00:10:23.409 --> 00:10:24.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yes, it is.</b></Default>

00:10:26.039 --> 00:10:27.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>RASCAL DOES NOT DREAM
OF SANTA CLAUS</b></Default>

00:10:29.450 --> 00:10:30.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yoshiwa.</b></Default>

00:10:30.700 --> 00:10:32.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You can solve that problem</b></Default>

00:10:32.120 --> 00:10:33.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>with what we talked about
earlier.</b></Default>

00:10:34.330 --> 00:10:37.409 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Come on, Mr. Sakuta</b></Default>

00:10:37.500 --> 00:10:40.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hold on a second.
After I'm done with Yoshiwa.</b></Default>

00:10:40.289 --> 00:10:41.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hey, Yamada, you want me</b></Default>

00:10:41.700 --> 00:10:43.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-to teach you some things?
-What?</b></Default>

00:10:43.370 --> 00:10:45.409 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's a bit
of a harsh reaction.</b></Default>

00:10:45.500 --> 00:10:48.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No, I didn't mean that
like I didn't want you to.</b></Default>

00:10:48.659 --> 00:10:50.159 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Okay, then I'll teach you.</b></Default>

00:10:51.080 --> 00:10:52.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[Yamada whimpers]</b></Default>

00:10:52.120 --> 00:10:54.909 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You see, this problem here
isn't about cosine theorem.</b></Default>

00:10:55.000 --> 00:10:58.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If you use the sine theorem</b></Default>

00:11:00.620 --> 00:11:02.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Himeji, you shouldn't go</b></Default>

00:11:02.370 --> 00:11:04.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>teasing your classmates
too much, all right?</b></Default>

00:11:05.000 --> 00:11:06.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Are you talking about Yamada?</b></Default>

00:11:06.830 --> 00:11:08.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And Yoshiwa as well.</b></Default>

00:11:08.500 --> 00:11:11.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Wow. You really care
about your students, don't you?</b></Default>

00:11:11.539 --> 00:11:13.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If the two of them
don't improve their grades</b></Default>

00:11:13.450 --> 00:11:15.159 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll be in serious trouble.</b></Default>

00:11:15.250 --> 00:11:16.409 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I understand.</b></Default>

00:11:16.500 --> 00:11:19.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll stop so I don't get
you in trouble.</b></Default>

00:11:19.620 --> 00:11:21.909 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That being said</b></Default>

00:11:22.039 --> 00:11:24.659 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>have you properly finished up
the homework I gave you?</b></Default>

00:11:28.120 --> 00:11:31.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>How about we chat outside?
I'm pretty hungry.</b></Default>

00:11:31.120 --> 00:11:32.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

00:11:32.120 --> 00:11:33.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I've been wanting
the new doughnut</b></Default>

00:11:33.370 --> 00:11:35.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>at the cafe
across from the station.</b></Default>

00:11:35.200 --> 00:11:36.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Care to treat me?</b></Default>

00:11:40.000 --> 00:11:42.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So, how are you going to spend
Christmas this year?</b></Default>

00:11:42.450 --> 00:11:44.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Like, do you have
anything fun planned?</b></Default>

00:11:44.500 --> 00:11:46.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If things turn out
like that dream we had</b></Default>

00:11:46.909 --> 00:11:48.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm gonna end up
going on a date with you.</b></Default>

00:11:48.909 --> 00:11:50.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Don't you think it's naughty</b></Default>

00:11:50.080 --> 00:11:52.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>for you to be meddling
with one of your students?</b></Default>

00:11:52.580 --> 00:11:53.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Still, though</b></Default>

00:11:53.580 --> 00:11:55.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I wonder why we were together
in the first place.</b></Default>

00:11:55.909 --> 00:11:57.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's what I'd like to know.</b></Default>

00:11:57.870 --> 00:11:59.409 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Do you have any ideas?</b></Default>

00:11:59.830 --> 00:12:02.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I think Mr. Sakuta was cheating
on his girlfriend.</b></Default>

00:12:03.200 --> 00:12:05.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, sure. That's totally it.</b></Default>

00:12:05.289 --> 00:12:07.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Please don't sound so sarcastic.</b></Default>

00:12:13.000 --> 00:12:14.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hmm?</b></Default>

00:12:14.120 --> 00:12:15.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hmm?</b></Default>

00:12:15.120 --> 00:12:17.409 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh! [chuckles]</b></Default>

00:12:19.539 --> 00:12:20.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You know them?</b></Default>

00:12:20.700 --> 00:12:23.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah. That girl's a friend
from my class.</b></Default>

00:12:23.370 --> 00:12:25.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And the guy with her is
a second-year who I worked with</b></Default>

00:12:25.700 --> 00:12:27.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>on the committee
for the sports festival.</b></Default>

00:12:38.500 --> 00:12:41.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Himeji, do you have history
with that boy?</b></Default>

00:12:41.950 --> 00:12:44.909 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, wow. Nothing gets
past you, Mr. Sakuta.</b></Default>

00:12:47.620 --> 00:12:49.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Mmm, tasty!</b></Default>

00:12:50.250 --> 00:12:51.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If you must know</b></Default>

00:12:51.330 --> 00:12:53.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>he asked me to date him
about two months ago.</b></Default>

00:12:53.830 --> 00:12:55.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And what was your reply?</b></Default>

00:12:55.659 --> 00:12:58.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I rejected him saying I couldn't
date him at this point in time.</b></Default>

00:12:58.950 --> 00:13:00.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>"At this point</b></Default>

00:13:01.080 --> 00:13:02.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But wasn't that
kind of horrible?</b></Default>

00:13:02.620 --> 00:13:04.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I mean, it's only been
two months.</b></Default>

00:13:04.450 --> 00:13:06.409 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Personally, I think
it's healthier for him</b></Default>

00:13:06.500 --> 00:13:08.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to get over you quickly
and move on</b></Default>

00:13:08.409 --> 00:13:10.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>if there's no hopes
of you looking his way.</b></Default>

00:13:10.700 --> 00:13:12.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Is it even possible
to be so practical</b></Default>

00:13:12.830 --> 00:13:14.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>after telling someone
you love them, though?</b></Default>

00:13:14.909 --> 00:13:17.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, if that's how
you feel about it</b></Default>

00:13:17.120 --> 00:13:18.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>then are you still in love
with Kasai?</b></Default>

00:13:21.250 --> 00:13:22.659 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You talked to Tora.</b></Default>

00:13:22.750 --> 00:13:23.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, sorry.</b></Default>

00:13:24.000 --> 00:13:26.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I mean, Kasai said something
to you, didn't he?</b></Default>

00:13:26.580 --> 00:13:28.659 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He said you were
childhood friends</b></Default>

00:13:28.750 --> 00:13:30.159 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and he's worried about you.</b></Default>

00:13:30.250 --> 00:13:31.159 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's very sweet</b></Default>

00:13:31.289 --> 00:13:33.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but I think he should be
more concerned for himself.</b></Default>

00:13:33.830 --> 00:13:34.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He went and fell in love</b></Default>

00:13:34.870 --> 00:13:37.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>with a difficult person
like Miss Futaba.</b></Default>

00:13:37.289 --> 00:13:38.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm sure she'll just dump him.</b></Default>

00:13:39.370 --> 00:13:42.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Though Kasai seems like
he's quite the popular type.</b></Default>

00:13:42.080 --> 00:13:43.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And a great guy.</b></Default>

00:13:43.620 --> 00:13:45.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah, he's a really great guy.</b></Default>

00:13:45.370 --> 00:13:47.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I mean, I'm someone
that he dumped</b></Default>

00:13:47.120 --> 00:13:49.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and yet he's still
worrying about me.</b></Default>

00:13:49.700 --> 00:13:51.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Although when I found out</b></Default>

00:13:51.330 --> 00:13:54.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that the person he was
really in love with wasn't me</b></Default>

00:13:54.620 --> 00:13:56.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>it made me hate him.</b></Default>

00:13:56.830 --> 00:13:58.909 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Honestly, I was shocked.</b></Default>

00:13:59.370 --> 00:14:02.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Everyone at school would say
we looked good together</b></Default>

00:14:02.080 --> 00:14:04.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and talked as if we were
an official couple.</b></Default>

00:14:04.700 --> 00:14:07.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>After that, I felt like
the world I had seen until then</b></Default>

00:14:07.200 --> 00:14:08.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>was all one big mistake</b></Default>

00:14:09.289 --> 00:14:11.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and I couldn't believe
in anything.</b></Default>

00:14:11.450 --> 00:14:13.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I felt uneasy
just stepping outside.</b></Default>

00:14:14.039 --> 00:14:15.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You mentioned before</b></Default>

00:14:15.200 --> 00:14:17.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that this was around
Golden Week, right?</b></Default>

00:14:17.250 --> 00:14:18.159 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yes.</b></Default>

00:14:18.250 --> 00:14:20.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Then you developed
puberty syndrome</b></Default>

00:14:20.580 --> 00:14:23.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and that uneasiness got
completely resolved somehow?</b></Default>

00:14:23.370 --> 00:14:24.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's right.</b></Default>

00:14:24.450 --> 00:14:27.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Is the fact that you've been
popular with guys recently</b></Default>

00:14:27.289 --> 00:14:28.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>because of that, too?</b></Default>

00:14:28.700 --> 00:14:30.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Wow, Mr. Sakuta</b></Default>

00:14:30.409 --> 00:14:33.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>you really did your homework
properly, didn't you?</b></Default>

00:14:33.200 --> 00:14:36.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Surprisingly</b></Default>

00:14:36.120 --> 00:14:37.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But you are incorrect.</b></Default>

00:14:37.830 --> 00:14:39.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Being super popular</b></Default>

00:14:39.080 --> 00:14:41.409 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>isn't the nature
of my puberty syndrome.</b></Default>

00:14:41.500 --> 00:14:44.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I do think I'm more popular now
than before, though.</b></Default>

00:14:44.330 --> 00:14:47.659 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So, you mean you're having fun
even with puberty syndrome?</b></Default>

00:14:48.039 --> 00:14:49.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Tell me, Mr. Sakuta</b></Default>

00:14:49.370 --> 00:14:51.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>do you not like me
being popular with guys?</b></Default>

00:14:51.700 --> 00:14:54.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No, I don't dislike it
or anything.</b></Default>

00:14:54.159 --> 00:14:55.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But realistically</b></Default>

00:14:55.580 --> 00:14:57.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>even if dozens of people
ask you out</b></Default>

00:14:57.700 --> 00:15:00.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and hundreds of people
fawn over you</b></Default>

00:15:00.120 --> 00:15:01.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>it's more than likely
that you won't be able</b></Default>

00:15:01.909 --> 00:15:04.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to obtain
what you really want, Himeji.</b></Default>

00:15:04.120 --> 00:15:05.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What is that supposed to mean?</b></Default>

00:15:05.950 --> 00:15:08.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I told you, I'm tremendously
happy right now.</b></Default>

00:15:08.370 --> 00:15:10.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There's nothing I want
in particular.</b></Default>

00:15:10.620 --> 00:15:13.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm sure being super popular
does have its benefits</b></Default>

00:15:13.830 --> 00:15:16.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but I believe there is something
more fortunate.</b></Default>

00:15:16.909 --> 00:15:18.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And what's that, exactly?</b></Default>

00:15:19.080 --> 00:15:21.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I think it's being with
the person I love the most</b></Default>

00:15:21.830 --> 00:15:24.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and knowing that I'm the person
they love the most.</b></Default>

00:15:27.700 --> 00:15:29.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Let me ask you again.</b></Default>

00:15:29.659 --> 00:15:30.659 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Be honest, Himeji.</b></Default>

00:15:30.789 --> 00:15:33.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Do you think you're still
in love with Kasai?</b></Default>

00:15:35.000 --> 00:15:35.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Even more than that</b></Default>

00:15:36.700 --> 00:15:39.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>were you even in love with Kasai
to begin with?</b></Default>

00:15:42.120 --> 00:15:43.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Is this your way of telling me</b></Default>

00:15:43.620 --> 00:15:45.409 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that I'm in the same boat
as Kasai?</b></Default>

00:15:45.500 --> 00:15:46.409 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>To be fair</b></Default>

00:15:46.539 --> 00:15:48.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>kind of looks like you thought
you were a good couple</b></Default>

00:15:48.620 --> 00:15:50.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>only because
other people said so.</b></Default>

00:15:51.039 --> 00:15:52.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Then tell me one more thing.</b></Default>

00:15:53.659 --> 00:15:54.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I wanna know</b></Default>

00:15:54.830 --> 00:15:57.659 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>how can I love someone
like you do, Mr. Sakuta?</b></Default>

00:15:58.289 --> 00:16:01.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>DECEMBER 12TH</b></Default>

00:16:02.289 --> 00:16:03.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MAI] Hmm.</b></Default>

00:16:03.289 --> 00:16:06.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So you ended up teaching her
romance very attentively</b></Default>

00:16:06.450 --> 00:16:08.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>down to the minute details.</b></Default>

00:16:08.159 --> 00:16:10.159 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I didn't go into any detail.</b></Default>

00:16:10.250 --> 00:16:12.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Sakuta, weren't you trying
to figure out</b></Default>

00:16:12.620 --> 00:16:15.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>what the nature of that girl's
puberty syndrome was?</b></Default>

00:16:15.120 --> 00:16:16.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>All for my sake?</b></Default>

00:16:16.620 --> 00:16:17.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah, I was</b></Default>

00:16:17.870 --> 00:16:19.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>because Mai is in danger.</b></Default>

00:16:19.450 --> 00:16:21.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So how does it end up that way?</b></Default>

00:16:21.620 --> 00:16:23.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Whatcha talking about?
-Hmm?</b></Default>

00:16:23.789 --> 00:16:26.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>About what falling in love
with someone is exactly.</b></Default>

00:16:27.039 --> 00:16:28.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Sounds philosophical.</b></Default>

00:16:28.620 --> 00:16:31.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You think so? It's instinct.</b></Default>

00:16:31.409 --> 00:16:34.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But what made you two
start a conversation like this?</b></Default>

00:16:34.659 --> 00:16:35.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The question was posed</b></Default>

00:16:35.789 --> 00:16:38.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>by one of Sakura's cute
new students at cram school.</b></Default>

00:16:38.830 --> 00:16:39.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Ah.</b></Default>

00:16:40.159 --> 00:16:42.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I kind of get where
she's coming from, though.</b></Default>

00:16:42.539 --> 00:16:45.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I sometimes wonder
what love really is.</b></Default>

00:16:45.250 --> 00:16:48.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What exactly about Azusagawa
do you love, Mai?</b></Default>

00:16:48.620 --> 00:16:50.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>How he loves me so immensely.</b></Default>

00:16:51.659 --> 00:16:53.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's, like, a truth.</b></Default>

00:16:55.159 --> 00:16:57.409 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MITO] I must say</b></Default>

00:16:57.500 --> 00:16:59.659 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>How she has boys
at her beck and call?</b></Default>

00:16:59.750 --> 00:17:01.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No, I mean, more like</b></Default>

00:17:01.330 --> 00:17:04.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>how she's enjoying the jealousy
she gets from other girls.</b></Default>

00:17:04.369 --> 00:17:06.869 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It shows that she really
loves herself that much.</b></Default>

00:17:07.369 --> 00:17:09.869 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>More than she loves anyone else</b></Default>

00:17:10.250 --> 00:17:13.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I think she fell in love
with the idea of being loved</b></Default>

00:17:13.500 --> 00:17:16.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>more so than actually falling
in love with someone else.</b></Default>

00:17:16.369 --> 00:17:19.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's quite the comment from
a popular girl like you, Mito.</b></Default>

00:17:19.539 --> 00:17:22.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I am a woman who can
see the differences, so, yeah.</b></Default>

00:17:22.829 --> 00:17:24.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Then what do you think
I should do here?</b></Default>

00:17:24.789 --> 00:17:26.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Should I interpret that as</b></Default>

00:17:26.579 --> 00:17:28.119 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>"How do I tell my cute student</b></Default>

00:17:28.200 --> 00:17:30.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>how to be able to love someone
the same way I do?"</b></Default>

00:17:30.539 --> 00:17:31.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Right.</b></Default>

00:17:31.869 --> 00:17:34.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I think you should make her fall
in love with you, Azusagawa.</b></Default>

00:17:35.039 --> 00:17:36.119 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[chuckles]</b></Default>

00:17:37.079 --> 00:17:39.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah, 'cause that will end well.</b></Default>

00:17:39.119 --> 00:17:41.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Be careful to not end up
as her third teacher</b></Default>

00:17:41.410 --> 00:17:43.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>who's outed
as a massive pervert.</b></Default>

00:17:43.289 --> 00:17:45.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] The only one
I'm devoted to is Mai.</b></Default>

00:17:45.579 --> 00:17:47.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MITO] Is that really so?</b></Default>

00:17:47.079 --> 00:17:49.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If you think about it</b></Default>

00:17:49.579 --> 00:17:51.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>nothing but your cute student
all day.</b></Default>

00:17:51.910 --> 00:17:54.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Is that not exactly
what she's been going after</b></Default>

00:17:54.500 --> 00:17:56.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Mr. Azusagawa?</b></Default>

00:18:00.160 --> 00:18:01.369 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>DECEMBER 14TH</b></Default>

00:18:01.450 --> 00:18:03.119 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>SHONAN PERSONAL INSTRUCTION
CRAM SCHOOL</b></Default>

00:18:04.539 --> 00:18:05.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hey, Yamada.</b></Default>

00:18:05.829 --> 00:18:06.869 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's unlike you.</b></Default>

00:18:07.450 --> 00:18:09.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're usually the first
to go home after class.</b></Default>

00:18:10.660 --> 00:18:11.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Mr. Sakuta</b></Default>

00:18:12.039 --> 00:18:14.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>you have a special class for
Himeji after this, don't you?</b></Default>

00:18:14.869 --> 00:18:15.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah.</b></Default>

00:18:15.910 --> 00:18:18.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But that's because she's on
a different level from you two.</b></Default>

00:18:19.700 --> 00:18:22.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Is Himeji dating someone
right now?</b></Default>

00:18:22.660 --> 00:18:24.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If you want to know
the answer to that</b></Default>

00:18:24.250 --> 00:18:26.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>you'll have to ask
Himeji herself, not me.</b></Default>

00:18:26.539 --> 00:18:28.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I can't ask her that.
That's why I'm asking you.</b></Default>

00:18:28.910 --> 00:18:30.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Mr. Sakuta.
-[Yamada gasps]</b></Default>

00:18:30.369 --> 00:18:31.619 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Can I come in?</b></Default>

00:18:32.039 --> 00:18:33.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Perfect timing.</b></Default>

00:18:33.410 --> 00:18:36.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yamada here has something
personal he wants to ask you.</b></Default>

00:18:36.369 --> 00:18:37.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Wait, Mr. Sakuta!</b></Default>

00:18:38.369 --> 00:18:40.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[stammers] It's nothing, really.</b></Default>

00:18:40.369 --> 00:18:41.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm gonna go home now.</b></Default>

00:18:41.869 --> 00:18:43.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, Yamada.</b></Default>

00:18:43.619 --> 00:18:44.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

00:18:44.910 --> 00:18:47.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So you know, I'm not dating
anyone right now.</b></Default>

00:18:47.750 --> 00:18:49.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But there is someone
who's caught my eye.</b></Default>

00:18:50.910 --> 00:18:52.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's all. Bye-bye!</b></Default>

00:18:53.369 --> 00:18:55.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That bit earlier</b></Default>

00:18:55.289 --> 00:18:57.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>for dragging me into
that conversation, you know.</b></Default>

00:18:57.829 --> 00:18:59.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm not accusing you for that.</b></Default>

00:18:59.539 --> 00:19:02.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But you were looking at me
like, "You did it again."</b></Default>

00:19:05.329 --> 00:19:06.369 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If I can solve this</b></Default>

00:19:06.450 --> 00:19:08.869 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>will I be able to fall in love
with people the way you do?</b></Default>

00:19:09.000 --> 00:19:11.869 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, actually, it'll prove
your current academic level.</b></Default>

00:19:12.000 --> 00:19:12.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hmm.</b></Default>

00:19:13.000 --> 00:19:14.369 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[inaudible]</b></Default>

00:19:16.039 --> 00:19:18.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Now, then, to explain
from the first question--</b></Default>

00:19:18.869 --> 00:19:21.119 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, so you used
that formula, right?</b></Default>

00:19:21.200 --> 00:19:23.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Right. This function
has nothing to do with it.</b></Default>

00:19:24.000 --> 00:19:27.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That question sort of reminds me
of you, Mr. Sakuta.</b></Default>

00:19:27.869 --> 00:19:30.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I think I have a much better
personality, though.</b></Default>

00:19:30.619 --> 00:19:33.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But that brazen part of you
is what's so appealing.</b></Default>

00:19:33.329 --> 00:19:34.869 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's why I like you.</b></Default>

00:19:36.200 --> 00:19:37.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>On to the next question.</b></Default>

00:19:38.000 --> 00:19:39.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>How could you move on and ignore</b></Default>

00:19:39.369 --> 00:19:41.119 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>a confession of love
from a student?</b></Default>

00:19:41.200 --> 00:19:42.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I don't dislike
how you also share</b></Default>

00:19:42.910 --> 00:19:44.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>those same qualities, Himeji.</b></Default>

00:19:44.579 --> 00:19:46.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Now, the next question.</b></Default>

00:19:46.579 --> 00:19:48.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This is, um... Well...</b></Default>

00:19:49.250 --> 00:19:51.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, Futaba. Hold on a sec.</b></Default>

00:19:51.119 --> 00:19:52.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What?</b></Default>

00:19:52.079 --> 00:19:54.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm having some trouble
with this question.</b></Default>

00:19:54.410 --> 00:19:56.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Would you mind explaining it
for me?</b></Default>

00:19:56.329 --> 00:19:57.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's a questionable statement</b></Default>

00:19:57.910 --> 00:19:59.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>from a cram school teacher</b></Default>

00:20:00.000 --> 00:20:01.119 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Help me out?</b></Default>

00:20:06.579 --> 00:20:08.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Do you get the gist of it now?</b></Default>

00:20:08.500 --> 00:20:09.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah, I get it.</b></Default>

00:20:09.579 --> 00:20:11.619 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're not the one I was asking.</b></Default>

00:20:11.700 --> 00:20:14.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yes. Your lesson
was very helpful.</b></Default>

00:20:14.079 --> 00:20:16.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Himeji, you must have
good grades</b></Default>

00:20:16.329 --> 00:20:18.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-outside of math as well, right?
-Huh?</b></Default>

00:20:18.750 --> 00:20:20.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If you had a proper instructor
teaching you</b></Default>

00:20:21.039 --> 00:20:23.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I think you'd get accepted
to a prestigious university</b></Default>

00:20:23.619 --> 00:20:24.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>as a high school third-year.</b></Default>

00:20:25.789 --> 00:20:28.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What is it you're trying
to say, sir?</b></Default>

00:20:28.289 --> 00:20:29.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What I mean is</b></Default>

00:20:29.289 --> 00:20:31.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Futaba is a much better teacher
than I am</b></Default>

00:20:31.329 --> 00:20:32.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and I'm sure you noticed too.</b></Default>

00:20:33.000 --> 00:20:34.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So having her teach you
might be better.</b></Default>

00:20:35.039 --> 00:20:37.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I want you, Mr. Sakuta</b></Default>

00:20:45.910 --> 00:20:47.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Is something wrong?</b></Default>

00:20:47.410 --> 00:20:48.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You guys okay?</b></Default>

00:20:49.039 --> 00:20:50.369 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>My apologies.</b></Default>

00:20:50.450 --> 00:20:52.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There was a question
that I didn't study up on</b></Default>

00:20:52.539 --> 00:20:55.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>so I had Miss Futaba
give me some assistance.</b></Default>

00:20:55.539 --> 00:20:56.619 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Is that so?</b></Default>

00:20:57.410 --> 00:20:58.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yes.</b></Default>

00:21:02.950 --> 00:21:04.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Thank you very much.</b></Default>

00:21:07.579 --> 00:21:08.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Uh...</b></Default>

00:21:09.579 --> 00:21:10.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Mmm?</b></Default>

00:21:13.869 --> 00:21:15.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FUTABA] You intentionally
made her angry.</b></Default>

00:21:15.869 --> 00:21:17.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What was the point of that?</b></Default>

00:21:17.750 --> 00:21:19.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] Long story short</b></Default>

00:21:19.160 --> 00:21:21.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>ultimately</b></Default>

00:21:21.579 --> 00:21:24.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>After all, you mentioned it
yourself the other day.</b></Default>

00:21:24.250 --> 00:21:26.619 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There's a chance that someone
who developed puberty syndrome</b></Default>

00:21:26.700 --> 00:21:27.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>because of Touko Kirishima</b></Default>

00:21:28.039 --> 00:21:29.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>could put Mai in harm's way.</b></Default>

00:21:29.789 --> 00:21:31.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FUTABA] And you think
that might be Himeji?</b></Default>

00:21:31.869 --> 00:21:34.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I can't say
that's the case for sure</b></Default>

00:21:34.119 --> 00:21:35.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but I still have no idea</b></Default>

00:21:35.250 --> 00:21:37.369 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>what kind of puberty syndrome
she has.</b></Default>

00:21:37.700 --> 00:21:39.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I was thinking
if I shook her up a bit</b></Default>

00:21:39.660 --> 00:21:42.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I might see a clue
for solving the issue.</b></Default>

00:21:42.079 --> 00:21:43.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But even so, is it just me</b></Default>

00:21:43.910 --> 00:21:46.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>or did it seem like she was
reacting rather excessively?</b></Default>

00:21:46.950 --> 00:21:49.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, that was
thanks to you, Futaba.</b></Default>

00:21:49.329 --> 00:21:50.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Uh, why?</b></Default>

00:21:50.579 --> 00:21:52.869 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>According to what
Himeji told me</b></Default>

00:21:52.950 --> 00:21:54.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>her puberty syndrome started</b></Default>

00:21:54.329 --> 00:21:56.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>right after she got rejected
by Kasai.</b></Default>

00:21:56.660 --> 00:21:57.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

00:21:59.039 --> 00:22:01.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If you're going to rope me
into a big mess like this</b></Default>

00:22:01.410 --> 00:22:03.369 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>explain why
you're doing so first.</b></Default>

00:22:03.500 --> 00:22:05.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>DECEMBER 15TH</b></Default>

00:22:08.539 --> 00:22:09.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[sighs]</b></Default>

00:22:09.750 --> 00:22:11.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I THINK MAI AND TOUKO
HAVE SIMILAR SINGING VOICES</b></Default>

00:22:11.789 --> 00:22:14.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There still isn't any
noteworthy information here.</b></Default>

00:22:15.539 --> 00:22:17.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yo, Azusagawa.
What you looking up?</b></Default>

00:22:17.789 --> 00:22:20.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Something tedious.
You, Fukuyama?</b></Default>

00:22:20.829 --> 00:22:23.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah, the Mr. and Miss Campus
contest at the school festival.</b></Default>

00:22:23.619 --> 00:22:25.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I found this website that
shows you all the winners</b></Default>

00:22:26.039 --> 00:22:28.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>from the festivals
of previous years.</b></Default>

00:22:28.250 --> 00:22:30.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So you were comparing
the previous winners</b></Default>

00:22:30.160 --> 00:22:31.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to see who was the cutest?</b></Default>

00:22:31.500 --> 00:22:33.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That was my plan originally.</b></Default>

00:22:33.829 --> 00:22:35.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But last year's Miss Campus</b></Default>

00:22:35.250 --> 00:22:37.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>doesn't have a profile
or picture on display.</b></Default>

00:22:37.829 --> 00:22:39.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The Mr. Campus does, though.</b></Default>

00:22:41.450 --> 00:22:42.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>See? Isn't it strange?</b></Default>

00:22:43.000 --> 00:22:45.869 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Fukuyama, are you saying
you can't see that?</b></Default>

00:22:45.950 --> 00:22:47.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Can't see what? It's blank.</b></Default>

00:22:47.910 --> 00:22:50.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>SOPHOMORE
MAJOR: INTERNATIONAL EDUCATION</b></Default>

00:22:51.250 --> 00:22:53.869 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Iwamizawa Nene?</b></Default>

00:22:55.450 --> 00:22:57.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[♪ closing theme song playing]</b></Default>

00:22:57.539 --> 00:23:04.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>RASCAL DOES NOT DREAM
OF HIS STUDENT</b></Default>

00:23:55.789 --> 00:23:57.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[HIMEJI] <i>Oh, Azusagawa</b></Default>

00:23:58.079 --> 00:24:00.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>NEXT EPISODE
#10 HOLY NIGHT</b></Default>
